{"analytics_identifier":"PB403","base_path":"/government/organisations/veterans-advisory-and-pensions-committees-x13","content_id":"dfe3c6ad-238b-4330-924a-33000e5b0df0","description":"We serve and support ex-servicemen and women, their widows or widowers and their immediate family members. We are an independent voice, here to help you whenever or wherever you served, whether in World War 2 or Afghanistan. VAPC is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Defence .","details":{"acronym":"VAPC","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We serve and support ex-servicemen and women, their widows or widowers and their immediate family members. We are an independent voice, here to help you whenever or wherever you served, whether in World War 2 or Afghanistan.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Veterans Advisory and Pensions Committees\">VAPC</abbr> is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence\">Ministry of Defence</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":null,"default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37da99e5274a79051c9162/s960_VAPC_logo.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37da99e5274a79051c9161/s300_VAPC_logo.jpg"},"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"Veterans Advisory and <br/>Pensions Committees"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/veterans-advisory-and-pensions-committees-x13/about/recruitment","title":"Working for VAPC"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/new-vapc-terms-of-reference-will-assist-all-veterans-and-their-families","image":{"alt_text":"Leo Docherty on poppy day","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/61cf0dddd3bf7f1f7036fb66/s712_London_poppy_day_2021.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publi