vall-VAPC-image.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2019-07-16T15:04:24.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>London VAPC (Veterans’ Advisory and Pensions Committee) welcomes appointment of Assembly member Len Duvall as informal armed forces champion.</p>\n</div>","title":"Armed forces champion for London announced as updated Veterans’ housing report published"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/more-than-a-third-of-the-capitals-boroughs-attend-workshop-on-housing-for-veterans","image":{"alt_text":"Left to right: Andrew Ross, Dr Edward Kirton-Darling, Professor Helen Carr, Neil Usborne, Alastair Williamson, Lynn Verity, Robert Money, Bruce Holborn, and Robert Rowntree. Copyright Paul Clabburn VAPC London.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5cf69f44ed915d0979296e8e/s712_VAPC-london-picture.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5cf69f44ed915d097064e789/s465_VAPC-london-picture.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5cf69f4440f0b60a15df3e85/VAPC-london-picture.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2019-06-04T15:44:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>London VAPC event brings together local authorities, armed forces charities and military support organisations.</p>\n</div>","title":"More than a third of the capital’s boroughs attend workshop on housing for Veterans"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/housing-workshop-for-veterans-to-be-hosted-by-london-vapc","image":{"alt_text":"Close up of a veteran's medals","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5cd587b240f0b6604fd5f731/s712_Veteran_medals.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5cd587b2e5274a3fdbf8c2b9/s465_Veteran_medals.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5cd587b240f0b660566c51a1/Veteran_medals.png"},"public_updated_at":"2019-05-10T15:08:23.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\